44
00:07:52,160 --> 00:07:55,840
Does it really teach us anything of his humility?

45
00:07:56,400 --> 00:08:04,160
Lest we forget, may we be reminded that our blessed Lord was as truly man as if he were never God.

46
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:07,920
And he was truly God as if he had never been man.

47
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:15,760
He was the only absolute sinless one.

48
00:08:16,640 --> 00:08:23,280
He knew no sin, and yet he took the place of dependence as a humble petitioner in prayer.

49
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:31,280
Ah, do we who are sinners take the place of full dependence upon him in humility?

50
00:08:32,160 --> 00:08:39,680
Or do we often depend upon ourselves and end up distressed and depressed and helpless?

51
