85
00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:19,520
Even though the New Agers in their perverted folks believe they become God and are a part of deity.

86
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:25,680
You might ask, how do we share in his acquired glory?

87
00:13:28,480 --> 00:13:33,920
We do so because we share the fruits of his saving work.

88
00:13:36,160 --> 00:13:42,960
Because of his work in Calvary, we attain this glory and have been made members of the body, the church.

89
00:13:45,520 --> 00:13:50,000
We have been made heirs and joine heirs with Jesus Christ.

90
00:13:51,280 --> 00:13:52,320
Of which he is made.

91
00:13:52,880 --> 00:13:58,480
We are members of the body of Christ, the pride of Christ.

92
00:13:58,800 --> 00:14:03,440
And then, of course, his word tells us that he shall reign, we shall reign with him.

93
00:14:03,760 --> 00:14:10,000
Thus we share in his acquired glory, but we worship and adore him in his essential glory.

94
00:14:10,560 --> 00:14:23,440
Looking now at verse 2, we read, As thou hast given him power over all flesh, that he should give eternal life to as many as thou hast given him.

95
00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:35,920
