96
00:14:36,480 --> 00:14:40,160
God has committed all authority unto the risen Christ.

97
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:44,960
And through his death and through his resurrection, he gives eternal life.

98
00:14:45,520 --> 00:14:58,320
In this uttered statement of our Lord here is his own recognition of his deity, because it is only as the divine one that he gives eternal life.

99
00:14:58,880 --> 00:15:02,080
Let us notice the last phrase of verse 2.

100
00:15:03,280 --> 00:15:06,160
As many as thou hast given him.

101
00:15:06,800 --> 00:15:12,400
Seven times, a similar expression of this phrase is used in this chapter.

102
00:15:12,720 --> 00:15:14,240
What does it suggest?

103
00:15:14,560 --> 00:15:22,320
