104
00:15:22,880 --> 00:15:24,080
And think of it, beloved.

105
00:15:24,240 --> 00:15:37,520
Every one of you, every one of you that has come to him by faith is one of those love gifts that God has given to his son because he bare our sins at Calvary.

106
00:15:38,080 --> 00:15:40,320
