107
00:15:40,640 --> 00:15:47,360
Jesus Christ paid the great price with his blood to wash and cleanse us filthy sinners.

108
00:15:47,920 --> 00:15:57,040
And then God looks down on every individual that will believe on his son by faith and then gives that one to his son as a love gift.

109
00:15:58,880 --> 00:16:03,680
My friend, have you ever received gifts for which you had to pay the price?

110
00:16:04,640 --> 00:16:06,320
This is what Christ did.

111
